---
layout: layouts/feature
style_src: career
permalink: career.html
title: Career History
description:
  Explore my complete career history, from education to work experience and hackathons. Discover the skills and 
  technologies I've mastered along the way.
heading_description: 
  This page covers my full professional journey—from my earliest roles to where I am today. It’s a complete record of 
  my work history and the milestones that have shaped my career in tech. For a curated selection of my most recent and 
  relevant experience, check out [my latest resume](/assets/files/resume.pdf).
---
  <article>
    {%- for section in career -%}
    <section>
      <div class="header-container timeline-grid">
        <i class="{{ section.icon }}" aria-hidden="true" role="presentation"></i>
        <h2>{{ section.heading }}</h2>
      </div>
      <ol{% if section.class %} class="{{ section.class }}"{% endif %} role="list">
        {%- for item in section.items -%}
        <li class="timeline-grid">
          <section aria-labelledby="item-{{ forloop.index0 }}-title">
            <header>
              <h3 id="item-{{ forloop.index0 }}-title">{{ item.title }}</h3>
              {% if item.subtitle %}
                <p class="subtitle">{{ item.subtitle }}</p>
              {% endif %}
              {% if item.date %}
                <p class="date">{{ item.date }}</p>
              {% endif %}
            </header>
            <div class="prose">
              {{ item.description | markdown | safe }}
            </div>
            {% if item.skills %}
            <ul class="bubble-list" role="list">
              {% for skill in item.skills %}
              <li>{{ skill }}</li>
              {% endfor %}
            </ul>
            {% endif %}
          </section>
        </li>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </ol>
    </section>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </article>